channel.title: You Me At Six - Hold Me Down
channel.description:
A 12 track album with their own unique style. Their first album was more pop/punk this is their own style and this is them trying to find themselves as musicians. Have a listen, i recomend: track 1 - The consequence track 2 - Underdog track 6 - Take your breathe away track 9 - Contagious chemestry
You can find this on youtube.... also the album artwork kicks ass!
